{"ts":"2026-04-27T12:35:00Z","op":"unlock-edit-relock","file":"tool/kick_dispatch.hexa","actor":"sub-W","change":"Added _detect_auth_failure(out) detector mirroring _detect_rate_limit_kind shape. Detects Anthropic 401 / invalid x-api-key / authentication_error patterns. Call site: after _detect_rate_limit_kind block in claude_code branch — if auth-fail detected, emit raw 66 trailer (4-step fix: refresh OAuth, cross-host sync, verify CLI-only migration, ref convergences) + fail-fast (exit 2) instead of rotating to next slot, since all slots on the same host share ~/.claude-claudeN OAuth dir family. Distinct from rate-limit (which has reset window).","reason":"Sub-W kick auth-failure surface — earlier ω-cycle attempt routed to ubu1 produced 401 invalid x-api-key from stale OAuth. Without explicit detection, kick exits with generic spawn-failed-rc-4 message that misleads operator. Need clear diagnostic trail for cross-host stale OAuth case.","authority":"raw 1 + raw 85 + raw 66 ai-native-error-message","convergence":"convergence/r4_kick_auth_fail_detection_2026_04_27.convergence","roadmap-ref":"R4_KICK_AUTH_FAIL_DETECTION","window_sec":0,"verified":"static grep verifies _detect_auth_failure fn body + 3 detection patterns + call site emits raw 66 trailer with 4-step fix"}
{"ts":"2026-04-27T12:50:00Z","op":"unlock-edit-relock","file":"/Users/ghost/core/hive/tool/subagent_dispatch.hexa","actor":"sub-Y","change":"_run_streaming_relay() poll loop: added idle-timeout watchdog. Track offset-advance ts each iteration; if (now - last_offset_advance_ts) >= idle_timeout_sec AND child PID alive AND .done sentinel absent, set idle_timed_out=true + break. After loop: distinguish idle_timed_out (rc=5) from sentinel_seen (rc=actual-pipeline-rc) and child-crash (rc=4). On idle-timeout: emit raw 66 4-step trailer (tail log / inspect extensions / extend env / ref convergence) + force-kill orphan child PID. Default timeout 600s (10min), configurable via HIVE_SUBAGENT_DRAIN_TIMEOUT_SEC env.","reason":"Sub-Y kick parent SSE drain hang — noise-envelope-module ω-cycle had child PID 27794 stay alive after agent.end was suppressed by hive-telegram extension stale-session warning. 22-min hang before manual SIGTERM. Bound the wall-clock cost with a UX-meaningful timeout while preserving 24h MAX_ITERS hard ceiling.","authority":"raw 1 + raw 85 + raw 66 + raw 80","convergence":"convergence/r4_kick_sse_drain_timeout_2026_04_27.convergence","roadmap-ref":"R4_KICK_SSE_DRAIN_TIMEOUT","window_sec":0,"verified":"static grep verifies idle_timeout_sec init / advance-tracking / break / rc=5 + 4-step trailer + force-kill"}
