utility paths short-circuit cleanly.","reason":"Sub-AB raw 44 (subagent-parent-propagation) hive infrastructure hardening: (a) concurrent hive sessions racing at PORT_LO=19877 — observed 4 stale node procs blocking port range low end, (b) ~/.hive/subagent-state inode anomaly — 0-byte regular file where directory expected, blocks concurrent writers, (c) stale orphan node procs leak when subagent crashes mid-relay — no recovery path. All three surfaced this session.","authority":"raw 1 + raw 44 + raw 66 + raw 80 + raw 85","convergence":"convergence/r4_subagent_dispatch_sub_ab_2026_04_27.convergence","roadmap-ref":"R4_SUBAGENT_DISPATCH_SUB_AB","window_sec":0,"verified":"hexa run tool/subagent_dispatch.hexa --selftest → __SUBAGENT_DISPATCH_SELFTEST__ PASS (5 fixtures: F-port up + down, F-state heal + dir-create, F-reclaim find + dry-run + real); hexa run tool/subagent_dispatch.hexa --reclaim-stale-ports --dry-run live → __SUBAGENT_RECLAIM__ PASS killed=0 kept=0 + auto-healed Mac state-root file→dir; standard usage error path emits expected raw 66 trailer post-relock"}
