{"ts":"2026-04-27T14:30:00Z","op":"unlock-edit-relock","file":"/Users/ghost/core/hive/tool/blocker_autofire.hexa","actor":"sub-AM","change":"_is_unsubstituted_template() filter + raw 66 trailer + skip — detects (a) filename suffix _template.hexa / .template / .disabled; (b) header name with literal '<>'; (c) fire-cmd containing <TOPIC> / <TOPIC_SLUG> / <BACKEND_SLUG> / <STRATUM_SLUG> / <AXES_CSV> / <WITNESS_DIR> / <DATE> / <YYYY-MM-DD> / <ID>; (d) slug with '<>'; (e) fire-cwd with '<>'. On hit: emit 4-step ai-native trailer + skipped++, no fire. Defense-in-depth: state/blockers/kick_template.hexa renamed → kick_template.hexa.template (glob *.hexa rejects). 52 orphan kick-<TOPIC_SLUG>.fires/ + attempts.jsonl + .pid cleaned.","reason":"Mac hexa_interp.real 41.83GB + 22.78GB runaway leak — kick_template.hexa was status=active in glob; blocker_autofire fired literal '<TOPIC>' as kick topic + literal '<TOPIC_SLUG>' as slug → 52 accumulated fires → multiple long-running hexa_interp.real on Mac → swap-out → screenshot Activity Monitor. Root cause: missing template filter at scanner-load time. Fix: 5-path filter (filename + name + cmd + slug + cwd) + raw 66 ai-native trailer per user directive 'return ai-native error message' + 'completely block recurrence'.","authority":"raw 1 + raw 36 fixpoint + raw 45 + raw 66 + raw 85","convergence":"convergence/r4_template_leak_filter_2026_04_27.convergence","roadmap-ref":"R4_TEMPLATE_LEAK_FILTER","window_sec":0,"verified":"selftest PASS; dry-run autofire fired=2 legit slugs / skipped template / 0 unsubstituted-<X> matches"}
